task.summary: Default task

Initial code check-in.
* core data in Subject class * persisted to MySQL using hibernate * wrote an excel parser * added supporting PharmGKB lib

Fixes.
* column count off by one * null check for splitter

Add directory crawling.
* can specify -d on the command line now to load all excel sheets in one dir
Move enums to their own package.

Updates.
* added metabolizer enum for metabolizer phenotype * fixed column number checking based on column headers * skip empty rows * added jUnit support

Updates.
* added metabolizer enum for metabolizer phenotype * fixed column number checking based on column headers * skip empty rows * added jUnit support

Fix SampleSource parsing.
* allow 0 as an "Unknown" value * throw errors if an unexpected SampleSource is found
Add more columns to the table for analysis.
Fix misspelling.

Add output file.
* now processing files generates output files that put "NA" in empty cells

Add dynamic column storage.
* since columns can't be depended upon to be in the same place or each project is not required to have the same columns
Correct how columns are crawled and more verbose log messages.
Fix logic errors, especially with NA values.
Add in definitions for sample properties.
new properties for more genotypes.
refactor project ID to be a number instead of a string.
Add in validation for property columns.

Don't validate creatinine levels.
* due to an email from Li saying project 5 can't express their creatinine levels numerically
clopidogrel and aspirin are not actually required.

Change way properties of subjects are persisted.
* take out most properties of Subject class, instead put them in as IcpcProperty instances * properties are pull from the IcpcProperty collection so the parser doesn't have to worry about column position
Change inter assay variation to not require a number, can be Strings.

Update data integrity checks.
* PPI names are now checked against an enum for consistency * hemoglobin and plasma urea are added for project 4

Make a combined data generator.
* generates a report that dumps all projects into one excel sheet with all columns * updated the apache POI lib to use streaming API for faster, more efficient report generation
Adding in javadocs.
Normalize spaces in property sql file.

Column header to property matching fixes.
* column names need to be normalized for whitespace * report should iterate through all possible properties, not just those for a given subject * update validation for columns, reflecting real world usage
Normalize genotype columns.

various fixes.
* add in known equivalents for self-reported and OMB races * remove duplicate ezetimib property * add new variant position properties
Update NA values and expand error message.
Add IDEA 12 prefs.
Add new columns from project 40 and ignore blank headers.
New columns and fix how unmatched columns are reported.
New columns for project 16.
Fix data bug.
Added code for parsing DNA file and properties for storing the found data.

Fix race reporting.
* don't show raw race data, show calculated fuzzy-matched race instead * new method for finding a best-match race to display * new Race enum

Various data format fixes.
* store "99" values as "NA" instead * get rid of duplicate "DNA concentration" property * alphabetize genotype bases for all rsid columns
Fix for time interval column.

More columns to skip number validation.
* these are time period columns and have mixed numbers and text
New column for picogreen concentration.

Output fixes and JavaDocs.
* now obey Property types when outputting the combined report, make number cells when needed * added more javadocs

Use double instead of floats for number values.
* POI expects doubles, not floats * fixes a bug for number display in the output file
new columns defs.
Put in data value check for new clopidogrel column.
Add config file.
New column definition.
More log info for exception.
Adding documentation.

Lot of changes.
* switched from MySQL to Postgres for various reasons * updated the Apache POI lib for dealing with excel files * filled in more JavaDocs on classes and methods * fixed the DDL for the project, especially property names * added an "analyze" option to check for consistency between all the property names in all the files * trimmed out some unused methods

Refactorings.
* renames Subject class to Sample class for more consistency * renames IcpcProperty to SampleProperty to make more sense * moved model object to a model package for organization

Refactored the database DDL.
* moved to the conf directory and renamed

Added index for sampleProperties.
* report generator was very slow without it.

Refactoring.
* should have moved with the rest of the model classes
Adding more indexes to the db.

Cleanup.
* clean out unused properties in Sample class * clean out unused properties in table DDL

Major update.
* move sample properties into a Map in the Sample class, remove old SampleProperty * put all properties into the Property enum * handle all validation as regex patterns in the Property enum * normalization is moved into the Property enum, now validation and normalization are two separate paths * expanded the number of Properties that are validated * cleanup some more references to MySQL * change hibernate to 4.2 version

Logging, indexing, update libs, and fix combined data report.
* update library jars for POI and logging * update to Logback logging instead of Log4j * fix combined data report to use the properties property of the Sample class properly * add index to properties tables so they work in decent time

Format descriptor.
* add in an addiitonal Property "format" property that describes the values in the property (comes from template) * stick the default template into the resources directory * start adding some formatting to the combined output file

Height normalization.
* fix obviously wrong height values.

BMI calculation.
* calculate the BMI for a sample if none is given and the necessary data is available

Add creatinine category.
* adding new property for creatinine category as requested 7/21 * creatinine category is now calculated from the creatinine measurement * creatinine category added to the submission template * combined data report now output columns in the order of the definition in the enum, not based on ID

Analysis fixes and javadocs.
* fix analyze, IcpcProperty no longer used, use Property instead * default constructor for ExcelParser uses the blank template file * column analysis gets written to the output directory now, with a timestamp * close outputstreams properly * loadFormats can manage its own db session * add more javadocs

Fix bug for blank columns.
* handle blank columns in the middle of the template properly
Fix ordering of columns in combined report.

Fix race and BMI.
* add fuzzy match for caucasians * make BMI miscalculations return NA
Post-process smoking status.
Post-process LVEF value and flag.
Post-process "time to event" and MI during follow-up.

Caucasiens, BMI, and LVEF.
* fix messpellings for caucasians * fix logic bug for BMI calculation of 0 value * Just set all missing LVEF values to 0 instead of NA
Caucasiens are still a problem.
Fix overzealous LVEF availability.
Add format text to propertyNames.
Update docs.
Added new columns for project 15.
Delete a sample if it exists before saving.

Parsing phenotype information.
* added new property enums for pheno information * added a parser for reading pheno information from a CSV file
Don't swallow exceptions.
New columns for project 40.
Update descrip for clinical setting.
Re-arrange columns re: 10/23/14 email from Li.

New Riken dataset parser.
* made a new Parser for data from Riken * refactored Dna parser to use same abstract class as Riken * added new Properties * fixed number validator to handle negative numbers

Rename columns and modified combined report.
* renamed two chronolog LTA columns as a correction * took out the property name from the combined report, was causing confusion.
IDEA config update.
